decQ2931TimerEntry.description: Each entry contains timers for one UNI / NNI. Note that the table is indexed by ATM ports (ifType = 'atm') as opposed to AAL5 entities (ifType = 'aal5'). Sorry about the cryptic timer names, but that's what the ATM Forum calls these timers in the UNI V3.0 Specification.
